w16cs350.controller.command

Class A_Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • w16cs350.controller.command.A_Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    A_CommandBehavioral, A_CommandCreational, A_CommandMeta, A_CommandMetaView, A_CommandStructural

    public abstract class A_Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the shared elements of a command, which is a command-pattern object used to queue up commands for execution.
